Live:- https://voting-system.ct.ws/ 
🚀 Features
👤 User Features

Register & Login

Update Profile

Upload Profile Photo

Vote Once

View Voting Results

🛠️ Admin Features

Add / Edit / Delete Candidates

Manage Users

View Contact Submissions

Election Analytics Dashboard

🖼️ Image Upload Support

Candidate Photos → uploads/candidates/

User Profile Photos → uploads/profiles/

📦 Installation Requirements

Install the following:
VS Code
XAMPP (Apache + MySQL)
phpMyAdmin

⚙️ Setup Instructions
Enable:

Apache

MySQL

3️⃣ Create Database in phpMyAdmin

Go to:

http://localhost/phpmyadmin


Create database:

voting_system

4️⃣ Import SQL

Copy the SQL in Database Structure (below) and paste into phpMyAdmin → SQL tab.

📁 Required Folders

Make sure these folders exist:

uploads/candidates/
uploads/profiles/


Add default image:

assets/default-profile.jpg

🔧 Database Configuration

Edit file:

config/db.php


Paste this:

<?php
$host = 'localhost';
$dbname = 'voting_system';
$username = 'root';
$password = '';

try {
    $pdo = new PDO("mysql:host=$host;dbname=$dbname;charset=utf8", $username, $password);
    $pdo->setAttribute(PDO::ATTR_ERRMODE, PDO::ERRMODE_EXCEPTION);
} catch(PDOException $e) {
    die("Database connection failed: " . $e->getMessage());
}
?>

🗄️ Database Structure (SQL Schema)

Paste this SQL into phpMyAdmin:

-- Create database
CREATE DATABASE IF NOT EXISTS `voting_system`
  DEFAULT CHARACTER SET utf8mb4
  COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci;

USE `voting_system`;

-- =========================
-- 1) users
-- =========================
CREATE TABLE `users` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `username` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `password` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `email` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `mobile` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `gender` enum('Male','Female','Other') DEFAULT NULL,
  `dob` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `nationality` varchar(22) DEFAULT NULL,
  `profile_photo` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `description` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `has_voted` tinyint(1) DEFAULT 0,
  `is_admin_dba` tinyint(1) DEFAULT 0,
  `created_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp(),
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  UNIQUE (`username`),
  UNIQUE (`email`),
  UNIQUE (`mobile`)
);

-- =========================
-- 2) candidates
-- =========================
CREATE TABLE `candidates` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `name` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `party` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `bio` text NOT NULL,
  `photo_url` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `votes` int(11) DEFAULT 0,
  `created_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp(),
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
);

-- =========================
-- 3) contacts
-- =========================
CREATE TABLE `contacts` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `name` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `gmail` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `mobile` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `description` text NOT NULL,
  `submitted_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp(),
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
);

-- =========================
-- 4) elections
-- =========================
CREATE TABLE `elections` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `election_date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp(),
  `total_votes` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `total_candidates` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `total_voters` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `snapshot_data` longtext,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
);

-- =========================
-- 5) votes
-- =========================
CREATE TABLE `votes` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `user_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `candidate_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `voted_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp(),
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `user_id` (`user_id`),
  KEY `candidate_id` (`candidate_id`),

  CONSTRAINT `votes_ibfk_1`
    FOREIGN KEY (`user_id`) REFERENCES `users` (`id`)
    ON DELETE CASCADE,

  CONSTRAINT `votes_ibfk_2`
    FOREIGN KEY (`candidate_id`) REFERENCES `candidates` (`id`)
    ON DELETE CASCADE
);

▶️ How to Run the Project

Move project folder into:

C:\xampp\htdocs\


Start Apache & MySQL

Open browser and visit:

http://localhost/voting-system/


Register → Login → Vote → View Results

